                            <img src="/images/icons/icons8-drum-96.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h4><a href="#" class="title-head mt-4 mb-2">Drum</a></h4>
                        <p class="text-para">Discover rhythm and percussion with dynamic drum lessons
                            designed to enhance coordination, timing, and musicality. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <div class="grids-1 box-wrap p-lg-3">
                        <div class="icon">
                            
                            <img src="/images/icons/icons8-violin-96.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h4><a href="#" class="title-head mt-4 mb-2">Violin</a></h4>
                        <p class="text-para"> Explore the beauty of the violin with personalized lessons
                            focusing on technique, musical expression, and repertoire. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-lg-5 mt-4">
                    <div class="grids-1 box-wrap p-lg-3">
                        <div class="icon">
                            <img src="/images/icons/pad.png" alt="">
