                        <p class="text-para"> Master the piano through comprehensive lessons tailored to
                            individual learning styles, covering technique, theory, and
                            repertoire
                            eos. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <div class="grids-1 box-wrap p-lg-3">
